        <h2 class="text-dark-400">Usability</h2>
        <p class="mt-8 font-bold">What is your innovation, and what specific problem or user need does it address?</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Generating concept images through AI rather than using real world materials. Simply.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Creating concept art is a time consuming and expensive process, each picture takes a lot of effort to produce, and most of them don't see the light of day. Our innovation aims to make this process more efficient. Our idea is to generate pictures using AI tools. The user gives the program a picture of a piece of furniture and in return gets the furniture in a new context, with new surroundings and a different appeal.</p>
        <p class="mt-8 font-bold">Who are your target users, and how will your innovation benefit them?</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Our target users are IKEA’s marketing section. Our innovation will help them lower cost on concept art generation, and also make it more time efficient. With AI-generated image they just have to take pictures of a product in an empty room and then upload it to KRAFT, KRAFT will then generate images based on the settings applied and give the user concept art in return.</p>
