    <!-- Feasibility -->
    <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-dark-400">Feasibility</h2>
        <p class="mt-8 font-bold">What are the potential barriers to implementation, including those related to sustainability, and how will you address them?</p>
        <p class="mt-4">
            The potential barriers to implementation of our solution is mostly caused by technical aspects. We do not have the time or the resources to train a model on strictly IKEA products or american kitchens. We also do not have powerful enough computers to generate really good pictures fast. These problems are close to impossible to completely solve for us, since they require resources we do not have. There should not be any real barriers related to sustainability since generating these pictures should always be more efficient than building a whole set etc. 
        </p>
